---
import MainLayout from '../../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
---

<MainLayout title="Main Goal">
    <section class="space-y-12">
        <header class="max-w-4xl">
            <p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-indigo-600 mb-3">
                Planning
            </p>
            <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-slate-900 mb-4">
                Main Goal
            </h1>
            <p class="text-lg text-slate-600">
                We aim to reduce vandalism and its financial impact by replacing high‑risk metal components
                with lower‑value materials that remain safe, compatible, and cost‑effective.
            </p>
            <br>
        </header>

        <div class="mx-auto max-w-5xl rounded-3xl border border-slate-200 bg-gradient-to-br from-indigo-50/50 via-white to-white p-6 md:p-12 shadow-xl shadow-indigo-500/5">
            <div class="flex flex-col gap-10 lg:flex-row lg:items-center lg:justify-between">

                <div class="flex-1 min-w-0"> <span class="inline-block px-3 py-1 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-indigo-600 bg-indigo-100/50 rounded-full mb-6">
                Strategic Goal
            </span>

                    <h2 class="break-words text-3xl md:text-4xl font-black text-slate-900 leading-[1.1] md:leading-tight">
                        Reduce vandalism incidents by 10% within 24 months
                    </h2>
                </div>

                <div class="flex shrink-0 items-center gap-4 sm:gap-6">
                    <div class="flex-1 sm:flex-none min-w-[130px] rounded-2xl bg-white border border-slate-100 p-6 text-center shadow-sm">
                        <div class="text-3xl font-black text-indigo-600">10%</div>
                        <div class="mt-2 text-[11px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-slate-400">Target</div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="flex-1 sm:flex-none min-w-[130px] rounded-2xl bg-white border border-slate-100 p-6 text-center shadow-sm">
                        <div class="text-3xl font-black text-indigo-600">24</div>
                        <div class="mt-2 text-[11px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-slate-400">Months</div>
                    </div>
                </div>

            </div>
        </div>

        <section class="space-y-4">
            <br>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900">Key Benefits</h2>
            <div class="grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-2">
                <article class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm">
                    <div class="text-indigo-600 text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] mb-2">Public Image</div>
                    <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-900">Better view for tourists and residents</h3>
                    <p class="text-slate-600 mt-2">Cleaner infrastructure improves how communities and visitors experience the area.</p>
                </article>
                <article class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm">
                    <div class="text-indigo-600 text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] mb-2">Service</div>
                    <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-900">Better water supply</h3>
                    <p class="text-slate-600 mt-2">Fewer disruptions lead to more reliable distribution across the network.</p>
                </article>
                <article class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm">
                    <div class="text-indigo-600 text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] mb-2">Security</div>
                    <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-900">Less vandalism</h3>
                    <p class="text-slate-600 mt-2">Lower-value parts reduce incentives for theft and sabotage.</p>
                </article>
                <article class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm">
                    <div class="text-indigo-600 text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] mb-2">Cost</div>
                    <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-900">Cheaper operation</h3>
                    <p class="text-slate-600 mt-2">Lower replacement and maintenance costs improve sustainability.</p>
                </article>
                <article class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm md:col-span-2">
                    <div class="text-indigo-600 text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] mb-2">Efficiency</div>
                    <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-900">Reduced material losses</h3>
                    <p class="text-slate-600 mt-2">Fewer stolen parts means less downtime and lower losses.</p>
                </article>
            </div>
            <br>
        </section>

        <section class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4">Objectives</h2>
            <div class="grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-2">
                <div class="rounded-xl bg-slate-50 p-4">
                    <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-500 mb-1">Objective 1</p>
                    <p class="text-slate-700">Reduce repair and replacement costs by 20% within 12 months through cheaper materials.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="rounded-xl bg-slate-50 p-4">
                    <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-500 mb-1">Objective 2</p>
                    <p class="text-slate-700">Retrofit at least 60% of high-risk sites with lower-cost materials within 24 months.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="rounded-xl bg-slate-50 p-4">
                    <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-500 mb-1">Objective 3</p>
                    <p class="text-slate-700">Decrease lifecycle costs by 15% across the network within 3 years.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="rounded-xl bg-slate-50 p-4">
                    <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-500 mb-1">Objective 4</p>
                    <p class="text-slate-700">Reduce average repair expenditure per incident by 25% within 2 years.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="rounded-xl bg-slate-50 p-4 md:col-span-2">
                    <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-500 mb-1">Objective 5</p>
                    <p class="text-slate-700">Ensure 80% of replaced infrastructure meets safety standards while limiting failure rate increases to ≤ 10% over 3–5 years.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
    </section>
</MainLayout>